article.headline: Alabama A&M 86, Prairie View 70
article.story: PRAIRIE VIEW, Texas (AP) -- Joe Martin scored 21 points and grabbed 17 rebounds to lead Alabama A&M to an 86-70 win over Prairie View A&M on Saturday night. Obie Trotter added 19 points for Alabama A&M (10-12, 8-7 Southwestern Athletic). Evan Hilton had 12 points, and Galen Gardenhire scored 11. Chris Gaines scored 24 points for Prairie View on 10-of-18 shooting. Phillip Scott added 15 points for the Panthers (4-22, 1-14).
